      <div class="bio-row">
        <div class="bio-photo reveal-left">
          <img src="images/photo2.jpeg" alt="Lohitha Sai Priya Ratakonda" onerror="this.src='images/photo3.jpeg'">
        </div>
        <div class="bio-content reveal-right">
          <p class="bio-text">Hey! I'm Lohitha Sai Priya Ratakonda, a Software Engineer with a strong background in Artificial Intelligence &amp; Machine Learning, full-stack development, and published research.</p>
          <p class="bio-text" style="margin-top:1rem">I have worked across telecom, fintech, and data science domains, building intelligent systems &mdash; from fraud detection platforms and graph neural networks to conversational AI and cloud-native applications. I bring both engineering depth and research curiosity to every project.</p>
          <p class="bio-text" style="margin-top:1rem">Outside of work, I love exploring new technologies and am always working on something new. I prefer to keep learning, continue challenging myself, and do things that matter.</p>
          <div class="bio-tags" style="margin-top:1.4rem">
            <span class="tag hi">Python</span>
            <span class="tag hi">PyTorch</span>
            <span class="tag hi">TensorFlow</span>
            <span class="tag hi">Spring Boot</span>
            <span class="tag hi">AWS</span>
            <span class="tag hi">LangChain</span>
          </div>
          <a href="images/Lohitha__Ratakonda__Resume.pdf" download class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:1.5rem;display:inline-flex">Download Resume</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="edu-section-label reveal-up">Education &amp; Certifications</div>

      <div class="cards-row" style="align-items:stretch;margin-left:-3.5rem;margin-right:-3.5rem;gap:1.5rem;">
        <div class="reveal" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:20px;">
          <img src="images/EDU_1.png" alt="Master of Science, Computer Science – Bowling Green State University" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:20px;transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);cursor:zoom-in;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:20px;">
          <img src="images/EDU_2.png" alt="Bachelor of Engineering, Computer Science – RMK College" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:20px;transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);cursor:zoom-in;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:20px;">
          <img src="images/EDU_3.png" alt="Cloud Certifications" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:20px;transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);cursor:zoom-in;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.06)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
