        <div class="card res-card reveal">
          <div class="res-num">01</div>
          <div class="card-title">Pneumonia Detection and Classification Using Chest X-Ray Images</div>
          <div class="res-journal">International Journal of Research and Analytical Reviews (IJRAR) &middot; 2024</div>
          <div class="card-body">Developed a computer-aided diagnosis system using CNNs and VGG16 transfer learning to classify pneumonia from chest X-ray images. Trained on 5,800+ images with data augmentation and normalization. Evaluated using confusion matrices, precision-recall curves, and ROC-AUC analysis &mdash; achieving 92% classification accuracy.</div>
          <span class="res-badge">Published &mdash; IJRAR, 2024</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card res-card reveal">
          <div class="res-num">02</div>
          <div class="card-title">Edge AI and Digital Twin for Autonomous Vehicles</div>
          <div class="res-journal">Master's Directed Research &middot; Bowling Green State University &middot; 2024&ndash;2026</div>
          <div class="card-body">Conducting a literature review of 15+ research papers on digital twin architectures and edge AI frameworks. Developing data pipelines for processing vehicle telemetry, performance metrics, and fault detection data. Explores federated learning and distributed ML inference across edge compute nodes.</div>
          <span class="res-badge upcoming">Upcoming Publication</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


